How to update the gwsumm-*.css files for gwsumm
=======================================================

To update the CSS files on the master branch:

- DO NOT EDIT the `/share/css/gwsumm*css` files directly!
- make changes to the core `/share/less/gwsumm.less` CSS file and commit
- run the make file::

    $ cd /share/less && make && cd ../css/

- and commit::

    $ git commit gwsumm*.css
